iew\">FTD</a>."]},"id":"f497cd3f-a147-4507-a540-f9c42a0e264f","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Payment &amp; Delivery"},"id":"d2cf7c9c-879e-4af1-8007-273a594813f8","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/jihLSA7roMHHQn8jmDf7E4.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"This company accepts credit cards, PayPal, American Express, Masterpass and Chase Pay. As with all gift baskets, the price you see on the website isn’t the price you’ll end up paying because of taxes and delivery fees.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/48859-harry-and-david31.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/jihLSA7roMHHQn8jmDf7E4.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"jihLSA7roMHHQn8jmDf7E4","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/jihLSA7roMHHQn8jmDf7E4.jpg","alt":""},"id":"cd8cdf3e-f4c3-4eb2-b32e-bfb85af66308","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["For an extra fee Harry &amp; David will ship overnight, and you can pay extra to have priority overnight shipping. You can also choose express shipping or regular ground shipping. If you are trying to send a gift to someone in the military, this company will deliver to APO/FPO addresses, something that not many other companies will do. You can also ship to some international destinations, including Canada, U.S. territories, Germany and the U.K.","One downside to using Harry &amp; David is there aren’t a lot of extras that you can include in your order. With many of the gift baskets and boxes, you can choose to include a bottle of wine, but other companies allow you to include greeting cards, stuffed animals, extra chocolates and other fun extras."]},"id":"c5249195-5031-47a1-88ca-fa72dfba9cab","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Help &amp; Support"},"id":"a7b77820-4806-45f0-83a3-0bd00b916769","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The 1-800-Flowers brand offers excellent customer service and an intuitive, easy-to-use website. There is a chat feature on the website that you can use to get help w